text:
Glad to find drink stalls after a walk in a hot afternoon.  So many selections, but stick to the basic cendol drink.  Reasonable price, $2 for good size.  Not too sweet, and the smaller cendol sipped through the normal size straw.  Happy with the purchase.

Will try other drinks in the future.

Our first time here at Empress Market Hawker Center,  the hawkers and cleaners were all so friendly and helpful that my friends and I each has such good experiences with them.
One of them is this Teh Tarik drink stall.  The boss was so smiley and nice and offer to serve the 3 drinks to our table for me.  We ordered the less sweet teh tarik, it was really good.  Will be back..
Was impressed by the wide variety of drinks sold at this stall. The price of the drinks were reasonable too.
Poor hygiene. Handled sugar cane immediately after handling money.
